<GUIClass name="CM_MenuEntityList" id="022c40a2-6447-49c1-9c5f-8c2731382506">
    <superclass name="Form"/>
    <transient/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <text>


This form lists all the CM_MenuEntities, including subclasses to view the icons and the root config key words used to store the icons.

It is used to view what classes have icons or not and whether the menu entities have the correct icons.

There are over 32,000 CM_MenuEntity objects so the method to lsit the objects has hard coded filters by sub class</text>
    <ImplicitInverseRef name="btnRefresh" id="9efc0d4a-9ae0-4a5f-aace-f2222cabaec8">
        <embedded/>
        <type name="Button"/>
    </ImplicitInverseRef>
    <ImplicitInverseRef name="tblMain" id="f0112f2a-c86e-4a0f-9fa2-d1a3de0a32e8">
        <embedded/>
        <type name="CM_Table"/>
    </ImplicitInverseRef>
    <JadeMethod name="btnRefresh_click" id="f642a3b0-487a-4ae1-8afc-d20c478307d2">
